{"tid":326633,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[ps4]Fifa Pro club 招人","createTime":"2017-07-18T07:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T15:35:02.000Z","uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed6566bebe17acf64b7b9645a25aa68b8e9c002","tid":326633,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱踢完vpl 而家同幾個朋友想離開原本隊伍 （d1隊伍）<br />\n而家重組一隊<br />\n而家招收翼衛(可翼可閘）中場 同 cb<br />\n歡迎大家試腳 留低tg <br />\n最緊要係聽人講 唔上腳 肯改善自身問題<br />\n如果係英雄主義 就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地踢法係控球在腳應快就快應慢就慢 亦都會斬波 唔得會回後 唔會夾硬隊前<br />\n反而防中真係會係防守駁腳轉邊較多<br />\n每晚10點零11點就會開波 <br />\n主要想搵full time 可以長時間踢<br />\n黎緊遲d都會參加 vpl expro 或者中國聯賽<br />\n希望大家一齊玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84591ea26107dc5c9a9ec08c6353818a9184c325","tid":326633,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db03f3c0df21bbbf34f9cb31fc8667785db1f1e5","tid":326633,"uid":5128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:56:26.000Z","msg":"11 點後我可以 psn:yin1232005"},{"pid":"1734a58f94c5a6b4eb6cc9a2e3b55c199eaeee29","tid":326633,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>11 點後我可以 psn:yin1232005</blockquote><br />\n搵左你了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc92b832fad638a3ccb38d9145a779e981f7f56","tid":326633,"uid":8112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"推推先"},{"pid":"e25b80c6d2afdd1e6cefc7e4f3324a9d5dfd8101","tid":326633,"uid":115545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"part time ok ??"},{"pid":"d94b74076eae8fbd8f7c85d778c6ef2eb72b9827","tid":326633,"uid":54241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-